title: My first note of 2021
body: Dear Node.js, I am taking a break from you to learn Swift, I promise I will be coming back to you in the coming years when everything makes sense and I am somewhat familiar with the Swift programming language. I will make sure to create at least one Node.js application by myself in the coming years. From Dante
